@startuml
!theme plain
title Прохождение теста студентом

actor "Студент" as Student
participant "TestingController" as Ctrl
participant "TestingService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Начало теста ==

Student -> Ctrl: GET /api/tests/{testId}/start
Ctrl -> Svc: StartAttemptAsync(testId, studentId, ct)
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM test_assignments\nWHERE test_id = @testId AND group_id = @studentGroup
DB --> Svc: TestAssignment
Svc -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM test_attempts\nWHERE test_id = @testId AND student_id = @studentId
DB --> Svc: attemptCount
alt attemptCount >= maxAttempts
  Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Fail(409, "Превышено количество попыток")
  Ctrl --> Student: 409 Conflict
else
  Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO test_attempts\n{ test_id, student_id, started_at }
  DB --> Svc: attempt
  Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok(attemptId)
  Ctrl --> Student: 200 { attemptId, durationMinutes }
end

== Получение вопросов ==

Student -> Ctrl: GET /api/tests/{testId}/attempt/{attemptId}
Ctrl -> Svc: GetAttemptAsync(testId, attemptId, ct)
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM test_questions\nWHERE test_id = @testId ORDER BY "order"
DB --> Svc: questions (shuffled if setting enabled)
Svc -> Svc: Strip correct_answers from response
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok({ questions, timeRemaining })
Ctrl --> Student: 200 JSON (questions without answers)

== Отправка ответов ==

Student -> Ctrl: POST /api/tests/{testId}/attempt/{attemptId}/submit\n{ answers: [...] }
Ctrl -> Svc: SubmitAttemptAsync(testId, attemptId, answers, ct)
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM test_attempts WHERE id = @attemptId
DB --> Svc: attempt
alt Time expired
  Svc -> Svc: Auto-submit, mark as timed out
end
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO test_answers\n{ attempt_id, question_id, answer, is_correct, score }
Svc -> Svc: Calculate total score & auto-grade closed questions
Svc -> DB: UPDATE test_attempts\nSET submitted_at = NOW(), score = @score, status = 'completed'
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok({ score, maxScore, passed })
Ctrl --> Student: 200 JSON (result)
@enduml
